# Download Android source with local_manifests
 Refer to http://source.android.com/source/downloading.html

 $ repo init -u https://android.googlesource.com/platform/manifest -b android-6.0.1_r13
 $ git clone https://github.com/Sulaiman2050/local_manifests .repo/local_manifests -b arpi-12
 $ repo sync

# Build for Raspberry Pi 3
 https://github.com/Sulaiman2050/device_brcm_rpi3

Use -j[n] option on sync & build steps, if build host has a good number of CPU cores.
